#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.array.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.array"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.array:1 of
msgid "Create a tensor."
msgstr "创建一个张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.array of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.array:3 of
msgid ""
"An array, any object exposing the array interface, an object whose "
"__array__ method returns an array, or any (nested) sequence."
msgstr ""
"一个数组，任何暴露数组接口的对象，其 __array__ 方法返回数组的对象，或任何"
"（嵌套）序列。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.array:6 of
msgid ""
"The desired data-type for the array.  If not given, then the type will be"
" determined as the minimum type required to hold the objects in the "
"sequence.  This argument can only be used to 'upcast' the array.  For "
"downcasting, use the .astype(t) method."
msgstr ""
"数组的期望数据类型。如果未给出，则将类型确定为保存序列中对象所需的最小"
"类型。此参数只能用于“向上转换”数组。如需向下转换，请使用 .astype(t) "
"方法。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.array:11 of
msgid ""
"If true (default), then the object is copied.  Otherwise, a copy will "
"only be made if __array__ returns a copy, if obj is a nested sequence, or"
" if a copy is needed to satisfy any of the other requirements (`dtype`, "
"`order`, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"如果为真（默认），则复制对象。否则，仅在 __array__ 返回副本、obj 为嵌套"
"序列或需要副本以满足其他要求（`dtype`、`order` 等）时才会进行复制。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.array:16 of
msgid ""
"Specify the memory layout of the array. If object is not an array, the "
"newly created array will be in C order (row major) unless 'F' is "
"specified, in which case it will be in Fortran order (column major). If "
"object is an array the following holds.  ===== ========= "
"=================================================== order  no copy"
"                     copy=True ===== ========= "
"=================================================== 'K'   unchanged F & C"
" order preserved, otherwise most similar order 'A'   unchanged F order if"
" input is F and not C, otherwise C order 'C'   C order   C order 'F'   F "
"order   F order ===== ========= "
"===================================================  When ``copy=False`` "
"and a copy is made for other reasons, the result is the same as if "
"``copy=True``, with some exceptions for `A`, see the Notes section. The "
"default order is 'K'."
msgstr ""
"指定数组的内存布局。如果对象不是数组，则新创建的数组将采用 C 顺序（行优先"
"），除非指定了 'F'，在这种情况下它将采用 Fortran 顺序（列优先）。如果对象"
"是数组，则遵循以下规则。===== ========= ================================="
"================== order  no copy                     copy=True ===== ==="
"====== =================================================== 'K'   "
"unchanged F & C order preserved, otherwise most similar order 'A'   "
"unchanged F order if input is F and not C, otherwise C order 'C'   C "
"order   C order 'F'   F order   F order ===== ========= ================="
"================================== 当 ``copy=False`` 并且因其他原因进行"
"复制时，结果与 ``copy=True`` 相同，但对于 `A` 有一些例外，请参见备注部分"
"。默认顺序是 'K'。"

